HEADWORD: Argentation
<hw>Ar`gen*ta"tion</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L. <ets>argentare</ets> to
silver, fr. <ets>argentum</ets> silver. See <er>Argent</er>.]</ety>
<def>A coating or overlaying with silver.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark>
<rj><au>Johnson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
